*** 7003,7017 ****
  Causes characters inserted or extracted after this call to be converted
  according to \&\f6loc\fP\& until another call of \&\f5imbue\fP.
  .nE
- .\" CD2-27-038. 27.8.1.4. Add effects for imbue
- .La "Effects:"
- Causes characters inserted or extracted after this call
- to be converted according to \&\f6loc\fP until another call of
- .CW imbue .
- .La "Note:"
- This may require reconversion of previously converted characters.
- This in turn may require the implementation to be able to reconstruct
- the original contents of the file.
  .\"----
